{"tid":1639686,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港警察變「綁匪」！隨街截停青年捉上7人車 將軍澳居民斥濫捕","createTime":"2019-10-08T16:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T04:06:33.000Z","uid":51620,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d0f8b30441a84fc6dabfc1422d9a902e0b9f8718","tid":1639686,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:38:42.000Z","msg":"警員漠視《警察通例》漸成常態，濫權濫捕更惹來全城怒火。昨晚（7日）將軍澳爆發警民衝突，有多名將軍澳街坊今早向《蘋果》反映，昨晚目擊一批警員在將軍澳運動場對出位置，疑「濫捕」年青居民。目擊事件的黃先生指出，將軍澳運動場一帶並非衝突現場，但昨晚10時左右，一批身穿防暴裝備的軍裝及疑為便衣警人士，駕駛多部7人車，一言不發如「綁匪擄人」般，帶走數名未滿20歲「街坊裝」年輕人，再驅車離開。黃指，當時他與其中一名被捕少女同由坑口出發，行到事發位置，對方全程未有任何可疑行為，但警員照樣將少女「挾上車」，明顯針對年輕居民，做法令人心寒。<br />\n<br />\n黃先生事發期間，由坑口經文曲里公園及將軍澳運動場，打算到爆發衝突的Popcorn商場一帶了解觀察情況。不過於將軍澳運動場及富康花園交界的路口，目擊警察如「綁匪擄人」般帶走年輕居民一幕。他說，昨晚約10時左右，當時現場並非衝突位置，10多名途人正準備過路。突然有3部7人車高速駛至，停車後10多名身穿防暴裝備人士衝落車，追向在場的2至3名年輕居民，以「拉、抬、夾」方式將其挾上車帶走。<br />\n<br />\n黃先生憶述，整個挾人過程歷時僅約半分鐘，其間只聽到車上傳來一句「X死你班仆街！」，車上另一人則高叫「鴻仔，冷靜啲！」全部疑為警員人士，落車後一言不發就帶走2至3名身型瘦削的少男、少女。黃續指，其中1名站在他身旁，被挾上車帶走的少女，當時僅穿「街坊裝」，未有帶任何隨身物品。當時與黃同樣由坑口出發行到事發位置，沿途未有做過任何可疑行為，「唔明白點解要好似綁匪綁人咁帶佢走」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191008/60131191?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0AyCi-Tn_rLhFosfrk5H0lh_2isF9X_GGP91hCPz0keI-QJiJQKcY4X6s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191008%2F60131191%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0AyCi-Tn_rLhFosfrk5H0lh_2isF9X_GGP91hCPz0keI-QJiJQKcY4X6s&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6ViF8jviwHHlsaTD6zKFHFMM%3D&h=e6d5411b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191008%2F60131191%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0AyCi-Tn_rLhFosfrk5H0lh_2isF9X_GGP91hCPz0keI-QJiJQKcY4X6s&h=6d60be1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191008/60131191?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0AyCi-Tn_rLhFosfrk5H0lh_2isF9X_GGP91hCPz0keI-QJiJQKcY4X6s</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qxr4P2v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqxr4P2v.jpg&h=410798fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9502a53dc02f0c9c2d7bb046a83905747f2c85c","tid":1639686,"uid":305009,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:39:21.000Z","msg":"濫捕非第一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2ed8f6481bcc6e6df82de64c3564e8df1f4da6","tid":1639686,"uid":51620,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e9502a53dc02f0c9c2d7bb046a83905747f2c85c","tid":1639686,"uid":305009,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:39:21.000Z","msg":"濫捕非第一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:41:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家唔係濫捕 係綁架"},{"pid":"7ceecb88a1987a8632ce5a864d94c60da1bd6c85","tid":1639686,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:45:52.000Z","msg":"（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a><br />\n<br />\n星期二（10月8日）早上，港鐵就宣布提前在晚上八點停駛，點解政府未卜先知出現動亂？其實政府有心製造一個長期嘅亂局，然後用緊急法立更多惡法，其中最近葉國謙就話要準備封網，呢樣嘢可以對香港抗爭造成極嚴重打擊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>斷網可毒啞香港人，新疆前車可鑑</ins></span></strong><br />\n斷網真係落實嘅話，<span style=\"color: red;\">最惡劣係好似新疆咁徹底斷網</span>，只有政府部門先可以上網，<span style=\"color: red;\">徹底封網的話，大家不但難以互通抗爭消息，而且香港訊息難以傳到海外，香港人也難以接收海外消息。西方人對香港嘅了解，只能經過政府嘅官方說法，或極少數流出嘅真相。</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">新疆早在2009年封網，同時限制境外人士到新疆旅遊，斷絕新疆對外聯繫，結果近年就出現新疆集中營。呢方面大家一定要警惕！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>大家不能掉以輕心</strong><br />\n或者有人認為政府會顧及香港嘅國際環境唔會輕易斷網，但現在中共已經失去理性，當中央黔驢技窮，損害香港利益而徹底封網並非不可。就好似半年前大家都唸唔到香港已經失去遊行以及戴口罩嘅自由。<br />\n<br />\n本文為節錄，全文請到此瀏覽：<br />\n<br />\n（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a>"},{"pid":"00db98d3d749d2b1d27bdd5cf070b0fe8a2c29d9","tid":1639686,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:53:29.000Z","msg":"繼續亂捉<br />\n等班藍絲同中立派睇清楚自己擁護緊咩"},{"pid":"48c9bac6575e1e77bc01f826e792f38a63e66304","tid":1639686,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:56:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc6fa84ac60d2df068ad6770f2ac8b44950c38f","tid":1639686,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00db98d3d749d2b1d27bdd5cf070b0fe8a2c29d9","tid":1639686,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:53:29.000Z","msg":"繼續亂捉<br />\n等班藍絲同中立派睇清楚自己擁護緊咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:58:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當到佢被綁架嘅時候 已經沒有人為我發聲了"},{"pid":"7d79e30cb6a4072b69b19df2ddc60ef37702bdf0","tid":1639686,"uid":305009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b2ed8f6481bcc6e6df82de64c3564e8df1f4da6","tid":1639686,"uid":51620,"like":